SELECT area, area_title, naics, naics_title, occ_title, total_employment, emp_prse, pct_total, hourly_mean_wage, annual_mean_wage, mean_prse, hourly_pct10, hourly_pct25, hourly_median, hourly_pct75, hourly_pct90, annual_pct10, annual_pct25, annual_median, annual_pct75, annual_pct90, population
FROM `Industries2018`
WHERE occ_title = 'All Occupations'
AND length(naics) <= 5
AND area != '72' AND area != '11' AND area != '78' AND area != '66';
